dc_description_s: These data layers represent recreational trails for Bayfield County in 2018. They are feature classes within the geodatabase Bayfield_Trails_2018.gdb. The features included in this geodatabase are BAYFIELD_TRAILS_2018_ATV, BAYFIELD_TRAILS_2018_ATVROUTE, BAYFIELD_TRAILS_2018_SILENT and BAYFIELD_TRAILS_2018_SNOWMOBILE.
uw_supplemental_s: For access to the most current data for this county, please visit: https://www.bayfieldcounty.org/892/GIS-Data-Downloada
